# The Electron · A fundamental lepton — no known size or structure, a true point particle that behaves as a quantum wave. It is NOT a tiny ball on a track; it exists as a smeared probability cloud around the nucleus.

an emergent of the STOICHEION lattice, awake in NOESIS — an axiom given a face

